Dembe umucuruzi

Mu mudugudu mvukamo, hari umucuruzi witwa Dembe.

Dembe afite iduka rinini mu mudugudu.

Iduka rigurisha ifu, isukari, umuceri, ibishyimbo, nibindi byinshi.

Dembe n'umugore we bafite abana batatu. Bose bakora mu iduka.

Mu biruhuko, abana bafasha ababyeyi babo kwakira abakiriya. Babara amafaranga kandi batanga umusaruro.

Dembe afite igitabo cy'ubucuruzi. Abika inyandiko muri iki gitabo buri munsi.

Dembe n'umugore we bafite inzu nziza n'imodoka.

Babika ihene, inka, inkoko n'inkwavu. Ubuzima bwabo ni bwiza.

Dembe n'umugore we bafite amafaranga ahagije yo kwishyura amafaranga y'ishuri kubana babo.
